</h2><h3 id="代理模式结构" class="heading-element"><span>2.1 代理模式结构</span>
  <a href="#%e4%bb%a3%e7%90%86%e6%a8%a1%e5%bc%8f%e7%bb%93%e6%9e%84" class="heading-mark">
